title: New Years in The Trap + Raphael Warnock Interview DCYoungFly Karlous Miller & Clayton English
itunes:title: New Years in The Trap + Raphael Warnock Interview DCYoungFly Karlous Miller & Clayton English
description:
This hilarious episode features a look back at 2020 - all the crazy things that happened all year AND THIS WEEK! DC young fly, Karlous Miller and Clayton English post up to talk about it all and laugh all the way through. - The internet confused Chico Bean with Baron Davis, Master P trying to buy Reebok....roasting Shaq and Morgan Freeman...this show is hilarious all the way through. The crew also talks about that Wack 100 fight!


PLUS, Chico Bean, Karlous Miller and DC Young Fly talk with Raphael Warnock and the importance of this upcoming Georgia senatorial run-off election. This is the coldest podcast!



Drop your favorite moments in the comments.
